subject: Can I count on your endorsement, Peter?
body: https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3[https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3] Peter, with the election threedays away , I’m really counting on my top supporters – that means you, Peter.Can I count on you to ENDORSE my campaign for Congress? I’ve been a leader onLBGTQ+ rights, veterans affairs, and AAPI advocacy – and I hope I’ve earnedyour support: » [https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3] ENDORSE MARKTAKANO FOR CONGRESS NOW » [https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3] My MAGAopponent wants to take a sledgehammer to our governmental institutions – hewants to ax the IRS, CDC, EPA, and MORE! Meanwhile, I’m working with myDemocratic colleagues to find ways to genuinely improve the lives of Americans– from labor rights to racial justice and more! But with out Democrats likeyou, we could LOSE the House majority once again AND the White House. SoPeter, can I count on your endorsement? With your help I can save this seat,take back the House Majority, and elect Kamala Harris to the White House »[https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3] 1,000 STRONG DEMOCRATS NEEDED:ENDORSE MARK FOR CONGRESS » [https://go.marktakano.com/a/endorse-mark3] Thankyou, thank you, thank you. -- Mark Takano----------------------------------------------- Paid for by Mark Takano ForCongress P.O. Box 5214, Riverside, CA 92517 www.marktakano.com Mark Takanorepresents the good people of California's Inland Empire in Congress, fightingfor the region's progressive priorities. He's been a voice for veterans,seniors, students, local businesses and hardworking families. But now,Republicans have captured a slim House Majority. The leadership of progressiveDemocrats like Mark will be critical to holding Republicans accountable andensuring the healing of our country during this challenging time.
